INFO 2025-05-08 13:01:31,262 documents 100 140080908453568 Chunks: ['## Republic of the Philippines ILIGAN INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY of the Mindanao State University\n\nOFFICE OF THE CHANCELLOR\n\niligan Address: A Bonifacio Avenue, 9200 Iligan City Telefax:\n\nManila Address: MSU-IIT MANILA INFORMATION & LIAISON OFFICE Bldg. 4 GSIS Metro Homes Tel.: Tel. (02) 716-3875\n\nTrunkline (063) 221-4050-55 (TL)\n\nOctober 11, 2010\n\n## MEMORANDUM ORDER No. 2010- 00231 -OC\n\n## SUBJECT: Designation of Ms. Joy A. Aban as Officer-in-Charge of the Office of the Vice Chancellor for Adail "as Officer-In-Charge of the\n\nIn view of the official travel of Dr. Polaus M. Bari, Vice Chancellor for Administration and Finance, Ms. Joy A. Aban, Institute Cashier, is hereby designated Officer-in-Chanse, thanse, this 30y A. Aban, Insulture Cashier, is hereby designated\nwithout additional compensation without additional compensation.', 'As such, she shall discharge all functions inherent to the position. She shall, however, refer matters which are policy making in nature with higher authorities.\n\nThis Order takes October 13, 2010 and shall remain in force until the return of Dr. Bari to the campus unless earlier revoked by competent authority.\n\n> FOR AND IN THE ABSSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\nOLGA M. NUNEZA, Ph.D.\n\nVice Chancellor Research and Extension & Officer-in-Charge']
