## SUBJECT: Grant of Permission to the Personnel of the MSU-IIT Liaison Office to Attend the MSU-IIT Charter Day Celebration in MSU-IIT on July 8 - 15, 2023

Permission is granted to the following staff of the MSU-IIT Liaison Office (MILO) to attend the MSU-IIT Charter Day Celebration in MSU-IIT and follow up on official matters on July 8-15, 2023:

- 1. Ms. Christy G. Dequit
- 2. Alexander M. Gaerlan
- 3. Gerardo C. Mabait
- 4. Sittie Noronehar D. Disocor

As such, the abovementioned personnel shall be entitled to transportation expenses, per diem, and the usual travel privileges, chargeable against MILO and OC funds, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.

This Order is effective on July 8-15, 2023, unless revoked by competent authority.

ALIZE ONEY M. DITUCAL Chancellor
