INFO 2025-05-08 23:54:36,459 documents 100 140262912935616 Chunks: ['Influencing the Future\n\nSeptember 4, 2024\n\nSPECIAL ORDER No. One 12 -IT Series of 2024\n\n## SUBJECT: Designation of Certain Personnel as Game Officials for the 56th Charter Day Celebration-Friendship Games\n\nIn view of the the request of the Sports Development Officer, the following personnel are designated as game officials for the various sports for the friendship games during the 56th Charter Day Celebration:\n\n- 1. Alejandro E. Retarta III\n- 2. Regie B. Jarantilla\n\nAs such, the above mentioned shall be entitled to honorarium, chargeable against Charter Day Funds.\n\nThis Order takes effect immediately.\n\nALIZEDNEY M. DITUSALAN University Chancellor']
